title: TCS Symantec to create analytics-driven security services
text:
TCS, Symantec to create analytics-driven security services 
Times Of India Friday 23rd October, 2015 
NEW DELHI: IT services major Tata Consultancy Services (TCS) today said it has partnered Symantec to provide analytics-driven security services. The partnership will enable customers to leverage business opportunities, reduce costs and improve productivity, TCS said in a statement....
